  "notes": "Fight from range, scout ahead, and let others know what your sharp eyes catch first. In melee only fair and lightly armored, but toughness keeps him standing longer than most expect. Odayla miracles and Rurik the shadowcat can change the shape of a fight quickly. Beast and Movement suit him better than crowded talky scenes.",
